### Get All products
GET http://localhost:3000/products HTTP/1.1

### Get All products
GET http://localhost:3000/products/2 HTTP/1.1

### Add a  product
POST http://localhost:3000/product HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "pid":8,
    "name":"product 8",
    "description":"description 8",
    "price":15,
    "category":"category 8"
