### Update   product
PUT http://localhost:3000/products HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "pid":8,
    "name":"product 8 updated",
    "description":"description 8  updated"
}

### DELETE  a  product
DELETE http://localhost:3000/products/8 HTTP/1.1